<lg met="elegaic"><lb n="1"/><l><w lemma="ὁ">τὸν</w> <w lemma="σοφός">σοφὸν</w> <w lemma="ὅδε">ἥδε</w><lb n="2"/><rs type="subject" key="city"><w lemma="πόλις">πόλις</w></rs> <persName key="Eupeithius" type="attested"><name nymRef="#Εὐπείθιος">Εὐπείθιον</name></persName><lb n="3"/><w lemma="ἕνεκα">εἵνεκα</w> <w lemma="πᾶς">πάντων</w></l><lb n="4"/><l><w lemma="ἵστημι">στήσατο</w> <w met="LAI/NEOS2" lemma="λαίνεος">λαϊνέ<hi rend="ligature">ην</hi></w><lb n="5"/><w lemma="εἰκών">εἰκόνα</w> <w lemma="δέμω">δειμαμένη</w> <g ref="#leaf"/></l><lb n="6"/><l><w lemma="μνάομαι">μνωομένη</w> <w lemma="μετά">μετὰ</w><lb n="7"/><w lemma="πότμος">πότμον</w> <w lemma="ὅτι">ὅτ'</w> <w lemma="ἀνήρ">ἀνδρά<lb n="8" break="no"/>σιν</w> <w lemma="αἶνος">αἶνος</w> <w lemma="ἀληθής">ἀληθὴς</w> <g ref="#leaf"/></l><lb n="9"/><l><w lemma="τίνω">τίνεται</w> <w lemma="ἀνδρόμεος">ἀνδρομέ<lb n="10" break="no"/>ης</w> <w lemma="ἔκτοθι">ἔκτοθι</w> <w lemma="βασκανία">βασκα<lb n="11" break="no"/>νίης</w> <g ref="#leaf"/></l>
</lg>
</div>
         <div type="translation">
            <p>This city had made and set up a stone image <supplied reason="subaudible">of</supplied> the wise Eupeithios because of everything, recalling that it is after death that true praise, beyond human envy, is accorded to men.</p>
         </div>
         <div type="commentary">
            <p>See discussion at <ref type="eAla-text" n="III.38" target=".xml"/>.</p>
         </div>
